Author: j4jackj
Text: Depressive eating disorder? Seems like an incipient EDNOS. Bring it up with someone. Ideally a therapist.

Author: Azaryxe
Text: It definitely sounds like there's some issues with food. We can't tell you whether it's an ED or not, but even disordered eating warrants getting help. Better to get it under control now before it morphs and takes over your life.
